## Development

### Local Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Py-Swift/MobileWheelsDatabase.git
cd MobileWheelsDatabase
pip install -e .
```

### Testing

```bash
# Build the demo site
mkdocs build

# Serve locally
mkdocs serve
```

